    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pale reddish-brown timber from the species Fagus grandifolia; it is hard, tough, fine-grained wood used for furniture, flooring, plywood, veneer, cooperage, shoe lasts, and tool handles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
